## 28. User Stories

### Public Tool User

As a job seeker, I want to check my ATS resume score for free so I can understand whether my resume needs improvement.

### Resume Match User

As a job seeker, I want to compare my resume against a job description so I can see if I am missing important keywords.

### Salary User

As a job seeker, I want to estimate salary by role, experience, and location so I can understand my market value.

### Resume Upload User

As a job seeker, I want to upload my existing resume so I do not need to create a profile from scratch.

### Master Profile User

As a job seeker, I want to edit my master profile so the AI uses accurate information.

### Tailoring User

As a job seeker, I want to generate a tailored resume so I can apply faster.

### Safe Tailoring User

As a job seeker, I want unsupported skills to be flagged so my resume does not include fake claims.

### Editor User

As a job seeker, I want to edit the resume before downloading so I control the final version.

### Paid User

As a paid user, I want to download my tailored resume as PDF so I can submit it to job applications.

### Tracker User

As a job seeker, I want to save every tailored resume to a dashboard so I know which resume I used for each company.

